<br>
But,He is suddenly knocked back as he recieves an arrow in his left shoulder.Losing his grip on the reign he falls back off of his winged steed,and plumets at-most 15 feet to the ground. Landing with a loud thud. &quot;Argh!&quot; He cringes in pain as he lands on his back,but quickly gains his sences as that tall amazon charges at him,plunging her sword toward his midsection. He quickly brings his sword up slicing the head of the spear off its shaft,then with another quick motion he jams the tip of his sword into the amazons gut.Lifting his left leg his kicks the amazon off his sword who then falls back,dead.<br>
<br>
Pegasus then lands swifty at his masters side,wings still open at full,the steed snorts and kicks at any on coming threat while Bellerophon stays down for the moment.<br>
<br>
Looking around quickly he keeps a watchful eye open for any threat and for the one who nailed him with an arrow. Seeing Pegasus holding back anyone,he takes hold of the arrow and snaps the shaft off with a wince,then tossing the arrow aside.<br>
<br>
Once gaining his sences fully,he stands up,grabbing hold of Pegasus' reigns and hoists himself back onto the saddle,and just as quickly as he mounted,Pegasus liftes them both back into the air.... <p>-=¤ Bellerophon ¤=-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 170<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(11/20/01 4:50:07 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/qhera.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ... The Battle Began ...</span><hr size=1> The Queen of the Gods had long held in interest in the amazons, as a patron diety and the fact they were women.  Her eyes narrowed as she watched the attack.  Attempting to hold back her powers and allow the amazons to fight off the enemy was not easy.  Then as Hera watched those amazons she was most close to charge into the bloodbath, her heart raced.  Sin's wish to join the fight was not hard to allow.  Hera, herself, was becoming harder to keep at bay.<br>
Slender pale fingers clenched into fists at either side of her black glittering gown.  White teeth bit hard together under slim red lips, and icy blue eyes watched with anger as amazons fell.  Even if the male soldiers fell...it was nothing to be joyous over.  Her heart sunk as she could feel each amazon who breathed their last breath.  How dare her brother attack the amazons?!  What did Poseidon think he had to prove?  These women rarely went near the sea..and they were certainly not seafarers. <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showMessage?topicID=8.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="